'''1929年大西洋飓风季'''的活跃度很低，一共只形成五个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，其中三个增强成飓风，一个达到[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]标准，即达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]的三级飓风或以上强度{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="ACE" />。全季首场风暴于6月27日在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]成型，次日成为飓风后[[登陆_(气象学)|吹袭]][[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]，在大面积地区产生狂风，共造成三人死亡，经济损失保守估计为67.5万美元{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有损失数额均为1929年[[美元|美元]]价值。|group="注"}}。

第二场风暴人称[[1929年巴哈马飓风|巴哈马飓风]]，在[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]北面形成，[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]高达每小时250公里，最低[[气压|气压]]924[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.3[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），达到萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级下的四级飓风上限，是全季最强烈的热带气旋。风暴以最高强度经过巴哈马，再经小幅减弱后袭击佛罗里达州，共夺走59条人命，经济损失至少236万美元。之后形成的三个气旋都没有影响陆地，最后一个于10月22日转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。气象学界此前八十年里一直认为本季只有四个热带气旋，但经2010年的[[大西洋飓风再分析计划|重新分析]]后认定最后一场风暴实际上是两个气旋。<ref name="documentation">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | title = Documentation of Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Changes in HURDAT | author = Christopher W. Landsea | date = 2012-12 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2017-01-03 | location = Miami, Florida | display-authors = etal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930195553/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_dec12.html | archivedate = 2015-09-30 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

这年飓风季的活跃程度还经累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]反映出来，数值为48<ref name="ACE">{{cite report | work = Hurricane Research Division; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-04 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425073956/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-12-24 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-04-25 }}</ref>。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高、持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高<ref>{{cite report |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |work=National Climatic Data Center |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-04-01 |location=Asheville, North Carolina |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html }}</ref>。

== 风暴 ==

=== 第一号飓风 ===
{{Infobox Hurricane Small
|Basin=Atl
|Image=1929 Atlantic hurricane 1 track.png
|Formed=6月27日
|Dissipated=6月30日
|1-min winds=80
|Pressure=982
